      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Are you sure?</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 text-sm leading-relaxed">
        This will permanently delete your account and remove all your data. This action cannot be undone.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
